com.portletguru.portlettester

Class TestResultHolder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.portletguru.portlettester.TestResultHolder

  • public class TestResultHolder
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is the container of the test results, such as the name/path of the PortletRequestDispatcher whose include/forward method has been called, the content of the PrintWriter has sent, etc.
